description:
When http://anidb.net/ch62131 [Keita] frees http://anidb.net/ch62128 [Whisper], a ghost-like youkai, from 190 years of imprisonment, Whisper pledges to protect Keita from supernatural dangers. Whisper also gives Keita a watch that allows Keita to see other youkai. Together with the twin-tailed cat spirit http://anidb.net/ch62131 [Jibanyan], they encounter many youkai-related problems and solve them.
Source: ANN
